== Kufala kwa Chilankhulochi ==
Chichewa ndi chimodzi mwa zilankhulo ziwiri zovomelezeka za [[dziko la Malawi]] (chilankhulo chinacho ndi [[Chingerezi]], ndipo Chinyanja ndi chimodzi cha zilankhulo zisanu ndi ziwiri za [[dziko]] la [[Zambia]], kumene chimalankhulidwa kwambiri kumvuma kwa dzikoli. Chichewa chimalankhulidwanso ku [[Mozambique]], makamaka mdera a [[Tete]] ndi [[Niassa]] ndiponso ku [[Zimbabwe]] kumene, malinga ndi kafukufuku, ndi chilankhulo chachitatu pa zilankhulo zonse za dzikolo, pambuyo pa [[Chishona]] ndi [[Chindebele]]. Maiko a [[Malawi]], [[Zambia]] ndi [[Mozambique]] ndi kumene chilankhulochi chmayankhulidwa kwambiri.
[[Baibulo]] (''Buku Lopatulika ndilo Mau a Mulungundi'', [[William Johnson]], 1912) ndi [[Korani]] anatanthauziridwa mu Chichewa.

== Mbiriasho ==
Chichewa chinayambira ku ufumu wa [[Amaravi]], umene unali wotchuka pa zaka za pakati pa 1500 ndi 1800. Ufumuwu unali ku Malawi, Zambia ndi Mozambique. Chilankhulochi chinakhalabe chotchuka ngakhale Angoni anagwetsa ufumu wa chi Maraviwo ndipo chinabvomerezedwa ndi ofalitsa uthenga wa [[Chikhristu]] pachiyambi pa [[chitsamunda.]]
[[Mtundu]] wa Achewa umapezeka pafupi ndi [[Nyanja ya Malawi]], choncho Chichewa chimatanthauza “Chilankhulo cha Achewa”. Ku Zambia, chilankhulochi chimatchuka ndi dzina lakuti [[Chinyanja]], lomwe limatanthauza “chilankhulo cha Anyanja”, ndipo chimalankhulidwa nsi anthu a Chingoni ndi Chikunda.
Mbali la [[Baibulo]] linatanthauziridwa mu chilankhulochi mu zaka za m’ma 1900.
